use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7829966\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7829966\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 16, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kpl1665703089347.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kpl1665703089347.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kpl1665703089347.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kpl1665703089347\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Maxtags </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the maximum number of tags that can be dynamically updated while typing in the ProcScript Editor. Valid values are whole numbers <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> and higher. The default is <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">20</code>.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kpl1665703089347__p_d105431e1_d105432e1_d105433e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n         \n                                maxtags\n                                <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kpl1665703089347__p_d105434e1_d105435e1_d105436e1\">This is a static property and can only be set in the initialization file.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kpl1665703089347__section_bmt_pjq_bcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d756832e77\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kpl1665703089347__p_d105440e1_d105441e1_d105442e1\">As you enter ProcScript, Uniface dynamically\n            updates the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tags</span> in the ProcScript Editor. If a trigger contains\n            many operations or entries, this can significantly degrade performance.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kpl1665703089347__p_d105443e1_d105444e1_d105445e1\">To prevent this, the  maxtags property defines the maximum number of operations, entries,\n            or triggers a development object can have before dynamic updates are stopped. In this\n            case, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tags</span> tree is not updated as you type, but it is updated\n            on other actions, such as cut and paste or new data being added to the object.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kpl1665703089347__p_d105446e1_d105447e1_d105448e1\">By default, the dynamic updates stop when the\n            number of entries, operations, and triggers is larger than 20. You can increase or\n            decrease this number by setting the property in the RichEdit widget in\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span>:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"kpl1665703089347__pre_t15_qjq_bcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[widgets]\n...\n; Custom widgets for development environment\nRichEdit=urichedit(font=procboxfont;procbox=on;maxtags=100)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7829966\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7829966\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Maxtags Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 16, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Maxtags Set the maximum number of tags that can be dynamically updated while typing in the ProcScript Editor. Valid values are whole numbers 0 and higher. The default is 20 . \" maxtags = Number \" This is a static property and can only be set in the initialization file. Description As you enter ProcScript, Uniface dynamically updates the Tags in the ProcScript Editor. If a trigger contains many operations or entries, this can significantly degrade performance. To prevent this, the maxtags property defines the maximum number of operations, entries, or triggers a development object can have before dynamic updates are stopped. In this case, the Tags tree is not updated as you type, but it is updated on other actions, such as cut and paste or new data being added to the object. By default, the dynamic updates stop when the number of entries, operations, and triggers is larger than 20. You can increase or decrease this number by setting the property in the RichEdit widget in usys.ini : [widgets] ... ; Custom widgets for development environment RichEdit=urichedit(font=procboxfont;procbox=on;maxtags=100) Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}